- [[Get All Google Cloud Storage Elements Buckets]] to get your TARGET<sub>BUCKET</sub>

``` shell
gcloud storage ls gs://TARGET_BUCKET
```

- you can also use a tool called `burf`
- see: [[List/Browse Google Cloud Storage GCS Bucket Using Burf]]
